In this project we use MPU-6050 module for checking robot angle.
MPU is 3-axis gyro, 3-axis accelerometer.

---------------- INFO -------------------

Supply voltage: 2.3 - 3.4V
Current: 5mA
Digital output: I2C @ 400kHz/100kHz
Logic supply voltage: 1.8V or VDD
ADC Resolution: 16-bit for each of 6 axes
Board size: 20.3x12.7x2.5mm
Mass: 0.9g

-----------------------------------------


